  {
    "title": "Shy Keenan",
    "body": "<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><strong><img class=\"wp-image-2024 alignleft\" src=\"/media-library/2017/06/small.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"96\" height=\"679\" srcset=\"/media-library/2017/06/small.jpg 190w, /media-library/2017/06/small-145x1024.jpg 145w, /media-library/2017/06/small-141x999.jpg 141w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 96px) 100vw, 96px\"></strong></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><em><strong><img class=\"wp-image-2140 alignleft\" src=\"/media-library/2017/06/15121624712065753787.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"159\" height=\"177\" srcset=\"/media-library/2017/06/15121624712065753787.jpg 415w, /media-library/2017/06/15121624712065753787-271x300.jpg 271w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 159px) 100vw, 159px\"></strong></em></span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><em><strong>Hello you :0) </strong></em>I really want us to start off on the right foot, so here’s a little bit more about me, before you just go&nbsp;right ahead ..and fall madly ‘in like’ with me.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">Born and broken in Birkenhead Merseyside (in 1963) I am described by many as ‘three times stronger than any household bleach’ ..mostly because of my natural born ‘Phoenix spirit’.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">Born Karen, changed&nbsp;to&nbsp;Peeta to hide from the abusers, then later to Shy&nbsp;to stand up to them. My abusers did not make me this strong, I was born this strong, they just tested that strength ..and lost.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><a href=\"/?p=2086\"><img class=\"wp-image-2054 alignright\" src=\"/media-library/2017/06/15121628521891091038-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"284\" height=\"195\" srcset=\"/media-library/2017/06/15121628521891091038-1.jpg 534w, /media-library/2017/06/15121628521891091038-1-300x206.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 284px) 100vw, 284px\"></a>I’m a housebound disabled wheelchair user (hip &amp; lung) who also manages&nbsp;Civilian Post Traumatic Stress, both&nbsp;act to limit my physical mobility in their own special ways, that said, I have full worldwide digital mobility via my ‘Virtual Office’.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><em><strong>“I started out with nothing and still have most of that left.”</strong>&nbsp;</em></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">As an orphaned broken kid in (don’t) Care, I came through the three metric inches of education I did get ‘completely uneducated’, but I’m a fast learning hard worker, who, despite the lifelong challenges&nbsp;..likes to use what bits of me still works, to earn my own way through life ..and as a person, if I’m ‘in the race’ I like to win,</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><em>As&nbsp;an adult Asexual, Areligious, Apolictical human female I am&nbsp;both passive and aggressive ..I’m&nbsp;Bi-Furious.</em></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><img class=\" wp-image-2028 alignright\" src=\"/media-library/2017/06/clong.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"98\" height=\"768\">Broken as I am, I still know the difference between right and wrong, good and bad and I work hard every day, to live a good life worth living, as a person who sincerely, wholeheartedly believes in that wonderful old saying&nbsp;..whatever doesn’t kill me …had better start running.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><strong>I believe all human people have good and bad in us</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong>..my faith is firmly placed in the good and potential good in me and in the good in others.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">I have come to learn&nbsp;that ‘the only way bad people prevail, is when good people do nothing, so I try hard not to be a nothing doer.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">I’ve also learnt that hate destroys everything,&nbsp;never fixes a thing ..that we can’t beat bad ‘with bad’, that the only way to stop it, is to find a way to tell ..and that the very best revenge, is to survive ..and survive well.”</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><img class=\"wp-image-2032 alignleft\" src=\"/media-library/2017/06/zAfXRRCD9X6GbTtJ76lHCw_r.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"434\" height=\"307\"></span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">Despite my lack of academia and the mobility&nbsp;challenges ..I went on to become an awarded advocate for those whose lives had been victimised by paedophile crimes ..awarded by the British Prime Minister, I was the first ever Britain’s Children’s Champion, I was one of Britain’s Bravest Women, a Most Inspirational Woman, a Wonder Woman and even a Woman Of The Year, also, a qualified Detective and an International Bestselling Author.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">I’m a respected&nbsp;AVP Consultant who works well with&nbsp;commercial companies/TV/Film/Media.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">I have some writer/song writing and artistic skills, I make model film sets and am currently developing an AR/VR App and Game.</span></p>\n<p><iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/kXU_zNzjgk8\" width=\"710\" height=\"400\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">For more about me and my Phoenix work .. <a href=\"http://www.thephoenixpost.com/shy-keenan-2000/\">click here</a> ..this is a work in progress, thank you for your patience :0) Shy ..nth</span></p>\n<div class=\"addtoany_share_save_container addtoany_content addtoany_content_bottom\"><div class=\"a2a_kit a2a_kit_size_16 addtoany_list\" data-a2a-url=\"/?p=1928\" data-a2a-title=\"Shy Keenan\"><a class=\"a2a_button_facebook\" href=\"https://www.addtoany.com/add_to/facebook?linkurl=%2F%2F%3Fp%3D1928&amp;linkname=Shy%20Keenan\" title=\"Facebook\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\"></a><a class=\"a2a_button_twitter\" href=\"https://www.addtoany.com/add_to/twitter?linkurl=%2F%2F%3Fp%3D1928&amp;linkname=Shy%20Keenan\" title=\"Twitter\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\"></a><a class=\"a2a_dd a2a_counter addtoany_share_save addtoany_share\" href=\"https://www.addtoany.com/share\"><img src=\"https://static.addtoany.com/buttons/share_save_171_16.png\" alt=\"Share\"></a></div></div>",
