    "title": "H&G AR/VR App/Game",
    "body": "<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #808080; font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>The House &amp; Garden&nbsp;AR/VR App/Game&nbsp;</strong>is essentially a&nbsp;management tool&nbsp;made for &amp; by those who manage Civilian Post Traumatic Stress.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #808080; font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><strong>Sep 2016</strong> – Giving our time voluntarily and with the help of our incredibly kind and wonderful ‘Phoenix Friends’ I started&nbsp;building a&nbsp;miniature version of our CPTS/Disabled friendly House &amp; Garden, to help us demonstrate (by design) how much more can be done for our kind, to be able to do much more for ourselves.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/LfSCjpIA2kg\" width=\"680\" height=\"315\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><strong>We’d never done anything like this before</strong>, however, once we got started, it was then quickly suggested that we turned the miniature model into a 360 AR/VR App/Game.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">We’ve never done anything like that before either, despite that, we agreed&nbsp;:0)</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><strong>With help and support from the very best mentors, we are </strong><strong>learning as we go and loving every bit of it and&nbsp;are sticking&nbsp;strictly to our&nbsp;‘Four P Plan’ to completion.</strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #000000; font-family: Calibri;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1981\" src=\"/media-library/2016/12/gameplan1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"680\" height=\"249\" srcset=\"/media-library/2016/12/gameplan1.jpg 1115w, /media-library/2016/12/gameplan1-300x110.jpg 300w, /media-library/2016/12/gameplan1-768x281.jpg 768w, /media-library/2016/12/gameplan1-1024x375.jpg 1024w, /media-library/2016/12/gameplan1-700x256.jpg 700w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 680px) 100vw, 680px\"></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #808080; font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><strong>September 2017 ..</strong>we are now working on raising the funds needed to ‘patent and develop’ the H&amp;G AR/VR App/Game so that we can sell it to&nbsp;game makers/distributors, we built the <strong>‘working playscale <a style=\"color: #808080;\" href=\"/?p=1880\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Phoenix Kitchen’ </a></strong>to help us do that,</span><span style=\"color: #808080; font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\"> we’ll update everyone as we go ..</span></p>\n<div class=\"addtoany_share_save_container addtoany_content addtoany_content_bottom\"><div class=\"a2a_kit a2a_kit_size_16 addtoany_list\" data-a2a-url=\"/?p=1833\" data-a2a-title=\"H&amp;G AR/VR App/Game\"><a class=\"a2a_button_facebook\" href=\"https://www.addtoany.com/add_to/facebook?linkurl=%2F%2F%3Fp%3D1833&amp;linkname=H%26G%20AR%2FVR%20App%2FGame\" title=\"Facebook\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\"></a><a class=\"a2a_button_twitter\" href=\"https://www.addtoany.com/add_to/twitter?linkurl=%2F%2F%3Fp%3D1833&amp;linkname=H%26G%20AR%2FVR%20App%2FGame\" title=\"Twitter\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\"></a><a class=\"a2a_button_google_plus\" href=\"https://www.addtoany.com/add_to/google_plus?linkurl=%2F%2F%3Fp%3D1833&amp;linkname=H%26G%20AR%2FVR%20App%2FGame\" title=\"Google+\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\"></a><a class=\"a2a_dd a2a_counter addtoany_share_save addtoany_share\" href=\"https://www.addtoany.com/share\"><img src=\"https://static.addtoany.com/buttons/share_save_171_16.png\" alt=\"Share\"></a></div></div>",
