    "title": "Shy Art & Animations",
    "body": "<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: book antiqua,palatino,serif;\"><strong>Using real objects, broken and remade, painted objects and photo filters, here are some&nbsp;stills taken from </strong></span><span style=\"font-family: book antiqua,palatino,serif;\"><strong>the ‘Broken Art’ Exhibit By Shy Keenan</strong></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-2221\" src=\"/media-library/2016/07/vzA0JKzhrKUjoDsYMNn0GQ_r-2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"690\" height=\"454\" srcset=\"/media-library/2016/07/vzA0JKzhrKUjoDsYMNn0GQ_r-2.jpg 700w, /media-library/2016/07/vzA0JKzhrKUjoDsYMNn0GQ_r-2-300x197.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 690px) 100vw, 690px\"></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: book antiqua,palatino,serif; font-size: 18pt;\"><strong>THE CATCHER</strong> </span></p>\n<p><img class=\"wp-image-2259 aligncenter\" src=\"/media-library/2016/07/Cq31PpcXgAAiKkU.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"690\" height=\"487\" srcset=\"/media-library/2016/07/Cq31PpcXgAAiKkU.jpg 981w, /media-library/2016/07/Cq31PpcXgAAiKkU-300x212.jpg 300w, /media-library/2016/07/Cq31PpcXgAAiKkU-768x543.jpg 768w, /media-library/2016/07/Cq31PpcXgAAiKkU-700x494.jpg 700w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 690px) 100vw, 690px\"></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em><strong>..Broken Art stills taken from the upcoming short animation..</strong></em></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1821\" src=\"/media-library/2016/07/1tt.jpg\" alt=\"Care Home Still\" width=\"690\" height=\"321\" srcset=\"/media-library/2016/07/1tt.jpg 2121w, /media-library/2016/07/1tt-300x140.jpg 300w, /media-library/2016/07/1tt-768x358.jpg 768w, /media-library/2016/07/1tt-1024x477.jpg 1024w, /media-library/2016/07/1tt-700x326.jpg 700w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 690px) 100vw, 690px\"></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18pt;\"><em><strong>(Don’t) Care Home</strong></em></span></p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-2269\" src=\"/media-library/2016/07/15124033231619039819.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"694\" height=\"578\" srcset=\"/media-library/2016/07/15124033231619039819.jpg 750w, /media-library/2016/07/15124033231619039819-300x250.jpg 300w, /media-library/2016/07/15124033231619039819-700x583.jpg 700w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 694px) 100vw, 694px\"></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18pt;\"><strong><iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/aKAUuJgmzK4\" width=\"689\" height=\"415\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe><br>\n</strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18pt;\"><strong>Paranoid Cammer By Shy Keenan</strong></span></p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-2248\" src=\"/media-library/2016/07/zz.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"701\" height=\"683\" srcset=\"/media-library/2016/07/zz.jpg 602w, /media-library/2016/07/zz-300x292.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 701px) 100vw, 701px\"></p>\n<p><strong>..this page is being updated, thank you for your patience, Shy ..coming up</strong></p>\n<div class=\"addtoany_share_save_container addtoany_content addtoany_content_bottom\"><div class=\"a2a_kit a2a_kit_size_16 addtoany_list\" data-a2a-url=\"/?p=1529\" data-a2a-title=\"Shy Art &amp; Animations\"><a class=\"a2a_button_facebook\" href=\"https://www.addtoany.com/add_to/facebook?linkurl=%2F%2F%3Fp%3D1529&amp;linkname=Shy%20Art%20%26%20Animations\" title=\"Facebook\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\"></a><a class=\"a2a_button_twitter\" href=\"https://www.addtoany.com/add_to/twitter?linkurl=%2F%2F%3Fp%3D1529&amp;linkname=Shy%20Art%20%26%20Animations\" title=\"Twitter\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\"></a><a class=\"a2a_dd a2a_counter addtoany_share_save addtoany_share\" href=\"https://www.addtoany.com/share\"><img src=\"https://static.addtoany.com/buttons/share_save_171_16.png\" alt=\"Share\"></a></div></div>",
