  {
    "title": "Shy Music",
    "body": "<p><img class=\"wp-image-1990 alignleft\" src=\"/media-library/2016/05/bwbuz.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"271\" height=\"209\" srcset=\"/media-library/2016/05/bwbuz.jpg 1080w, /media-library/2016/05/bwbuz-300x231.jpg 300w, /media-library/2016/05/bwbuz-768x592.jpg 768w, /media-library/2016/05/bwbuz-1024x789.jpg 1024w, /media-library/2016/05/bwbuz-700x539.jpg 700w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 271px) 100vw, 271px\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1787\" src=\"/media-library/2016/05/a1.jpg\" alt=\"Shy\" width=\"387\" height=\"214\" srcset=\"/media-library/2016/05/a1.jpg 1174w, /media-library/2016/05/a1-300x166.jpg 300w, /media-library/2016/05/a1-768x424.jpg 768w, /media-library/2016/05/a1-1024x565.jpg 1024w, /media-library/2016/05/a1-700x386.jpg 700w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 387px) 100vw, 387px\"></p>\n<p>Many years ago now, I&nbsp;performed as a singer in&nbsp;some incredible venues&nbsp;like&nbsp;‘The London Hippodrome’&nbsp;and the renowned ‘Jazz Café’.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/gb/album/whisper-to-wind-feat.-amata/id923038163\"><img class=\"wp-image-1346 aligncenter\" src=\"/media-library/2015/06/WTTW.jpg\" alt=\"WTTW\" width=\"667\" height=\"246\" srcset=\"/media-library/2015/06/WTTW.jpg 948w, /media-library/2015/06/WTTW-300x110.jpg 300w, /media-library/2015/06/WTTW-700x258.jpg 700w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 667px) 100vw, 667px\"></a></p>\n<p>My real passion is and has always been ‘song writing’. I’ve&nbsp;written, produced and&nbsp;arranged&nbsp;my own songs featuring some brilliant singers ..music&nbsp;is my happy place..</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<div class=\"addtoany_share_save_container addtoany_content addtoany_content_bottom\"><div class=\"a2a_kit a2a_kit_size_16 addtoany_list\" data-a2a-url=\"/?p=1527\" data-a2a-title=\"Shy Music\"><a class=\"a2a_button_facebook\" href=\"https://www.addtoany.com/add_to/facebook?linkurl=%2F%2F%3Fp%3D1527&amp;linkname=Shy%20Music\" title=\"Facebook\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\"></a><a class=\"a2a_button_twitter\" href=\"https://www.addtoany.com/add_to/twitter?linkurl=%2F%2F%3Fp%3D1527&amp;linkname=Shy%20Music\" title=\"Twitter\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\"></a><a class=\"a2a_dd a2a_counter addtoany_share_save addtoany_share\" href=\"https://www.addtoany.com/share\"><img src=\"https://static.addtoany.com/buttons/share_save_171_16.png\" alt=\"Share\"></a></div></div>",
