    "title": "The Phoenix Post",
    "body": "<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong><a href=\"http://www.thephoenixpost.com/\"><img class=\"wp-image-1673 alignleft\" src=\"/media-library/2016/05/ab11.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"109\" height=\"110\" srcset=\"/media-library/2016/05/ab11.jpg 794w, /media-library/2016/05/ab11-150x150.jpg 150w, /media-library/2016/05/ab11-298x300.jpg 298w, /media-library/2016/05/ab11-768x773.jpg 768w, /media-library/2016/05/ab11-360x360.jpg 360w, /media-library/2016/05/ab11-700x704.jpg 700w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 109px) 100vw, 109px\"></a></strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\"><strong>Digital Mobility </strong>Sara and I&nbsp;retired as advocates in 2017,&nbsp;we&nbsp;continue to work&nbsp;voluntariy&nbsp;for <a href=\"http://www.thephoenixpost.com/\">The Phoenix Post</a> (registered Not For Profit) with regards&nbsp;to our <a href=\"http://www.thephoenixpost.com/anti-victim-prejudice/\">#ThinkHuman</a> work&nbsp;and for the development of our House &amp; Garden AR/VR App/Game,&nbsp;a managemnt tool made for and by those who manage Civilan Post Traumatic Stress.</span></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.thephoenixpost.com/\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-2174\" src=\"/media-library/2016/05/bb1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1015\" height=\"514\" srcset=\"/media-library/2016/05/bb1.jpg 1015w, /media-library/2016/05/bb1-300x152.jpg 300w, /media-library/2016/05/bb1-768x389.jpg 768w, /media-library/2016/05/bb1-700x354.jpg 700w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1015px) 100vw, 1015px\"></a></p>\n<div class=\"addtoany_share_save_container addtoany_content addtoany_content_bottom\"><div class=\"a2a_kit a2a_kit_size_16 addtoany_list\" data-a2a-url=\"/?p=1451\" data-a2a-title=\"The Phoenix Post\"><a class=\"a2a_button_facebook\" href=\"https://www.addtoany.com/add_to/facebook?linkurl=%2F%2F%3Fp%3D1451&amp;linkname=The%20Phoenix%20Post\" title=\"Facebook\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\"></a><a class=