  {
    "title": "Love Is Love",
    "body": "<p><img class=\"wp-image-1909 alignleft\" src=\"/media-library/2015/06/themother.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"405\" height=\"278\" srcset=\"/media-library/2015/06/themother.jpg 776w, /media-library/2015/06/themother-300x206.jpg 300w, /media-library/2015/06/themother-768x528.jpg 768w, /media-library/2015/06/themother-700x482.jpg 700w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 405px) 100vw, 405px\"></p>\n<p>I feel I was blessed to become the parent of LGBTQ twins,&nbsp;the core centre of an unspeakable joy that came into my life when they did.</p>\n<p>As they grew into wonderful young&nbsp;human beings, that joy was very quickly accompanied by a deep sense of dread and foreboding for&nbsp;two kind and sweet&nbsp;little humans, just trying to find their place in a&nbsp;society that (to them) just wants to hate them out of existence.</p>\n<p><strong>My son Ayden was&nbsp;only just 14 years old </strong>..he was just trying to get an education when he was bullied out of living ..by socially groomed religious hate-filled homophobic bigotry and a systemic failure by the education authorities to protect our LGBTQ children at school.</p>\n<p>I understand that you can’t beat hate with hate (it likes it)&nbsp;for me, hating them back feels like surrender, my&nbsp;own personal faith in human good ..could never do that. So, we (Ayden’s family and friends)&nbsp;set about lawfully and peacefully trying to change things for the better.</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1516\" src=\"/media-library/2015/06/adlaw.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"982\" height=\"279\" srcset=\"/media-library/2015/06/adlaw.jpg 982w, /media-library/2015/06/adlaw-300x85.jpg 300w, /media-library/2015/06/adlaw-768x218.jpg 768w, /media-library/2015/06/adlaw-700x199.jpg 700w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 982px) 100vw, 982px\"></p>\n<p>So many good people&nbsp;stepped up to support the&nbsp;call for an ‘Ayden’s Law’.<img class=\"alignleft wp-image-1520\" src=\"/media-library/2015/06/adl3.jpg\" alt=\"adl3\" width=\"733\" height=\"201\" srcset=\"/media-library/2015/06/adl3.jpg 1190w, /media-library/2015/06/adl3-300x82.jpg 300w, /media-library/2015/06/adl3-768x211.jpg 768w, /media-library/2015/06/adl3-1024x281.jpg 1024w, /media-library/2015/06/adl3-700x192.jpg 700w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 733px) 100vw, 733px\"></p>\n<p><strong>Ayden’s Law&nbsp;– </strong>We did indeed have&nbsp;some wonderful support, but also, sadly, many broken promises by those we trusted. However, on this&nbsp;agonising journey, we had managed to change&nbsp;many minds and social policies&nbsp;along the way, that helped to bring about some of the&nbsp;positive changes happened for&nbsp;our LGBTQ children trying to get an&nbsp;education with fear,&nbsp;offering us some&nbsp;hope that his tragic death was not in vein.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Since Ayden’s death in&nbsp;2013,</strong> we have worked hard to make sure that real change is on the way ..there is so much more to say, just give us&nbsp;time, we’ll&nbsp;get there, Ayden’s family Good Bless</p>\n<div class=\"addtoany_share_save_container addtoany_content addtoany_content_bottom\"><div class=\"a2a_kit a2a_kit_size_16 addtoany_list\" data-a2a-url=\"/?p=1300\" data-a2a-title=\"Love Is Love\"><a class=\"a2a_button_facebook\" href=\"https://www.addtoany.com/add_to/facebook?linkurl=%2F%2F%3Fp%3D1300&amp;linkname=Love%20Is%20Love\" title=\"Facebook\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\"></a><a class=\"a2a_button_twitter\" href=\"https://www.addtoany.com/add_to/twitter?linkurl=%2F%2F%3Fp%3D1300&amp;linkname=Love%20Is%20Love\" title=\"Twitter\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\"></a><a class=\"a2a_dd a2a_counter addtoany_share_save addtoany_share\" href=\"https://www.addtoany.com/share\"><img src=\"https://static.addtoany.com/buttons/share_save_171_16.png\" alt=\"Share\"></a></div></div>",
